{"tid":749280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年底前薯條免費食 麥當勞優惠搶客","createTime":"2018-07-20T01:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T04:53:08.000Z","uid":18213,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"71894ad5e04b4e02a2e129223f0b21e2da2cd412","tid":749280,"uid":18213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"愛吃麥當勞的美國居民別錯過了，集團宣佈，即日起至年底，每逢周五都派發免費中薯條。<br />\n<br />\n要取得這項優惠，顧客必須先下載麥當勞手機應用程式，以獲取優惠券。在任何時候，使用該手機App，在麥當勞消費最少1美元，即可獲得一張免費中薯條換領券，次數不限。這張優惠券每周五都可以使用，活動舉行至今年年底12月30日。<br />\n<br />\n不喜歡吃薯條的話，麥當勞也有為細汽水推出相同優惠，逢周二和周四可以使用。其他手機應用程式限定優惠，還有1美元的雙層芝士孖堡，以及1美元購買任何大小咖啡等。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司/《薩克拉門托蜜蜂報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180720&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58463992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180720%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58463992&d=KR2iNJyhpgUPMk8BaXJNfdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a1d714b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180720%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58463992&h=090dc8d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180720&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58463992</a><br />\n<br />\n正 有得免費食薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295a9e16ee71274b33fb7c2e90f3d028e6e67ef5","tid":749280,"uid":54502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:58:18.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1aa455e3bf4c0765ce0e2ce1841757d0d5fef37","tid":749280,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"香港無咩用啦<br />\n之前出果個咩港式奶茶都有m記開頭都有免費派<br />\n結果咪又係得返廢老係到搶"},{"pid":"1b455623a9ab2d6931ad889700be7fe8d3a353f3","tid":749280,"uid":39800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1aa455e3bf4c0765ce0e2ce1841757d0d5fef37","tid":749280,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2